QuestData.Title: Scheduled Pickup
QuestData.Description: You've proven yourself more than capable in battle, $n. There may be Shadow Council forces all around Auchindoun, including near Telmor.$B$BI want you to join Soulbinder Tuulani at Telmor to make sure the crystal makes it safely to Auchindoun. I know I can trust you to get it done.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Soulbinder Tuulani outside Telmor.
QuestData.RewardText: It's not safe here. The Shadow Council has already taken the city!
